description: This is how it feels!    This is how it feels to put every ounce of your passion into an creative outlet and have your visions manifest into reality.    This is how it feels to be surrounded by a community who supports and believes in you. ...    This is how it feels to have a partner who loves you, and encourages you to live your life to its fullest unbridled expression.    This is how I feel... and I never hope to forget the overwhelming flood of gratitude and joy that I have been floating on since THIS moment.    In trying to describe it to my co-teacher  Gordon  Ogden, I said "This must be how it feels to 'stick the landing'. When all your years of dedication, practice, and passion boil down to a single moment; and all that left is to throw your hands up and do what you were born to do."    Thank you to the amazing teams at  Walter Productions  and  Walter Yoga  that made this moment possible, I could not have done it without you.     (Photo: Chris Patrick)   See More
